sentences: Luis Felipe Ram√≥n y Rivera (August 23, 1913 - October 22, 1993)  was a Venezuelan musician, composer and writer.
Director of several orchestras and the founder of The National Typical Orchestra, he was also for twenty years the director of the National Institute of Folklore.
